OL,3,CMum accused of murdering six-year-old
OL,4,Cson appears in court
OL,6,FA mum accused of murdering her young
OL,7,Fson and trying to murder her father
OL,8,Fhas appeared in court.
OL,10,FPolice were called to a house in the
OL,11,FGendros area of Swansea on Thursday,
OL,12,F29 August, where they found the body
OL,13,Fof six-year-old Alexander Zurawski.
OL,15,FKarolina Zurawska was subsequently
OL,16,Fcharged with murdering the boy and
OL,17,Ftrying to murder her father, 67-year-
OL,18,Fold Krzysztof Siwi.
OL,20,FBoth alleged offences are said to have
OL,21,Fhappened on the same day.
