OL,3,CMum accused of murdering six-year-old
OL,4,Cson appears in court
OL,6,FThe defendant appeared at Swansea
OL,7,FCrown Court via video link from HMP
OL,8,FEastwood Park on Thursday, 26
OL,9,FSeptember, where her barrister John
OL,10,FHipkin KC said preparations were in
OL,11,Fhand for a psychiatric report into his
OL,12,Fclient.
OL,14,FNo pleas have yet been entered in the
OL,15,Fcase and a further hearing will take
OL,16,Fplace on December 12.
OL,18,FKarolina Zurawska, aged 41, of Cwm Du
OL,19,FClose, Gendros, Swansea, will remain
OL,20,Fin custody until her next hearing.
