OL,6,FA provisional date has been set for
OL,7,FFebruary 17, 2025.
OL,9,FFollowing the death of Whitestone
OL,10,FPrimary School pupil Alexander, his
OL,11,Ffamily released a tribute to the
OL,12,Fyoungster.
OL,14,FThey said: "He loved playing with his
OL,15,Flittle sister and playing with his dog
OL,16,F'Daisy'. Alexander was always well
OL,17,F-behaved and never naughty.
OL,19,F"He was very clever and very mature
OL,20,Ffor his age. He had great
OL,21,Funderstanding of facts.
